"Randomly export controlled on a Friday night."

That is how fast access to a frontier model can vanish. No vote, no warning. One policy decision and the tool you built on is gone.

@jon_durbin on the fix: sovereign models owned by the network. No export controls, no regional https://t.co/ntPTGQKroF

Military strikes trigger rippling economic effects across the globe. 

With Numinous miners building the harnesses to forecast these influential events, traders can stay ahead with a dedicated military strikes model.

@lightningrodai delivers the specialist models outperforming https://t.co/nOKV5FkxHG

What does TPN actually look like in the real world?

@0xDutchmikel sat down to walk through the real world use cases for TPN.

From compressing models to run offline on a laptop, to fitting frontier AI onto a car's onboard chip, to cutting cloud inference bills exponentially. https://t.co/T2OTK7ErW4

